Yes I've noticed. Way too many directions? You mean in the "real" 
world right? Oh when can we start drowning ourselves in sake and 
actually make our fics come true... Cheers everyone! I want a hot 
one! :O)


--- In SHQ_Spy_Division@yahoogroups.com, spiritus saitou 
<spiritus_saitou@y...> wrote:
> Really glad to see you join us, wounds!!  I think we're all a 
little busy right now --- I know I've gone in way too many directions 
lately --- but I'm beginning to get back to my writing and hope 
others are, too.
>  
> Welcome to you and everyone else who's taken a place around the 
table.  Now, who's hogging all the sake???  ;-D
>  
> phil
> 
> Grace Battista <gracebattista@a...> wrote:
> Can't believe I missed this group. Hello minna! Most of the members

> 
> Umm... Just wanted to introduce myself first to be polite. 
> 
> mg_batt here from Miburo, edojidai and SHQ. My pen name is wounds 
in 
> fanfiction.net. Crazy about Saitou-sama and a fast growing interest

much

already

with

a
